  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>Synopsis:</i></strong><br><br>\t\tKappa's Asylum is a survival horror game in which you control a YouTuber in an<br>\t\tabandoned asylum to record a video.<br><br>\t\tYumi is a young woman who wants to be a famous YouTuber.<br>\t\tOne day Yumi receives a suggestion from her friend to go to the abandoned<br>\t\tasylum to record a video.<br><br><strong><i>Features:</i></strong><br><br>\t\t- This game is inspired by japanese urban legends.<br>\t\t- You are not a fighter, you have to run or hide to survive the enemies.<br>\t\t- Unpredictable Enemies: You cannot know when you will be surprised by enemies.",
